INSERT INTO `la_news` VALUES (5, 4, '时隔13年 世茂再续三里屯“工体”情缘', NULL, 'JORCO云资产', NULL, NULL, '<section><section><img class=\" __bg_gif\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/gULw5FTH7H5PibsZDMCAC8dC67nZnnYKWr3b9khhlrnIJR3J5mf9FFC0H4cXic1VkpjoJiaVcu4eT32ibbF9O3TGlA/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></section></section><p><br/></p><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2007年，世茂控股以人民币14亿元收购北京三里屯地区一综合地块，而后斥资30亿元打造集高档商业和甲级精装写字楼于一体的商业综合体，2016年，又以29.72亿元将核心商业部分世茂工三转让于乐视控股。至此，虽然世茂工三一直未曾更名，但世茂集团却与三里屯小别4年。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2020年4月26日，隶属中植系麾下的中海晟融对外公布成功收购北京市东城区核心地段的工人体育场西路公寓项目，也就是大家熟知的工体3号公寓。与此同时，小别4年的世茂集团又以40%股权加入，与中海晟融共同参与“工3”项目的改造与运营，至此，世茂再次重回三里屯商圈，续写与“工体”的再结情缘。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/gULw5FTH7H5PibsZDMCAC8dC67nZnnYKW6Z7WUcpCHWabhoYtpHib8Y1o16k73kUpWCSpGNobL70emAN1NU3O3qQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">世茂难以割舍的“工体”意义何在？</strong></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">想要知道世茂为何难以割舍“工体”，我们就要先来看看“工3”所处的环境优势。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“工3”位于朝阳区核心区域三里屯商圈，地处工人体育场西路，与北京工人体育场仅一街之隔，更与朝阳门商圈、东直门商圈形成“铁三角”，无论地理位置、商业氛围还是交通环境都属极佳，是一处集商务、居住、娱乐、消费物业形态为一体的建筑综合体。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(57, 157, 159);\">从交通位置看</span>，工体3号位于东二与东三环正中位置，南北距离均约1.5km，北邻工体北路，南接工体南路，距东直门驾车只需5分钟，距离机场约20分钟；对于商务人士而言，交通地理绝佳；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(57, 157, 159);\">从商务氛围看</span>，工3号被中央商务区、燕莎商圈、朝阳（外）商圈、使馆区四大财富区域环抱，云集各类金融、保险、政府机构、以及盈科、保利、港澳中心、等高端写字楼物业，多高端商务云集于此，机遇人脉更是可遇可求；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(57, 157, 159);\">从自然环境看</span>，工体3号所处的位置毗邻使馆区与工体，占有很多项目无法相比的自然环境优势，项目的北边，是工人体育馆经多年精心维护的大片成树原生环境；而使馆区更显得闹中取静，静中更显不凡，是繁华之中难得的一处幽静之地。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(57, 157, 159);\">从人文环境看</span>，工人体育馆经常举办重大体育赛事和娱乐演出，太古里更是靠人与自然结合的文化圣地，三里屯轻吧、工体的夜店更是囊括了各种性格和喜好的人与事，东西仅隔一个街区，却成为北京夜生活的地标。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><section><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/gULw5FTH7H5PibsZDMCAC8dC67nZnnYKWyZicgd6ibFXlzrvt6TNia7mxq0vfsuHIgVzO3AEuBXpKI732wEV0BymwQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">时隔3年，“工3”降价5亿重新易主</strong></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2016年世联行曾就“工3”项目进行价值评估，评估总价为17.12亿元，但时至今日，北京市整体房地产交易市场环比价格已上涨30%，本应该随波逐流的房价在“工3”面前却出现了跳水，中海晟融在公布成功收购“工3”项目时标注的成交价为12亿元左右，成交单价约为4.35万/㎡，这也在市场中引发了不小的争论。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">中植系与世茂此次联合收购“工3”项目，就目前来看，疫情期间无论何种地产业态的发展都面临着严峻的下滑势态，但从长远角度另观，疫情只是暂时的，“工3”项目自身的区域优势以及核心地段可供散售的70年产权公寓属性，“工3”项目无疑也是一个不可再生的稀缺资源。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">中植系与世茂的结合能否让沉寂的“工3”重放异彩</strong></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">中海晟融正是中植旗下的投资平台，主要针对战略投资、阳光私募、私募投资和并购重组业务等。自2016年以来，“工3”项目是中植系在北京成功收购的第2件大单，根据上一单以32亿收购的中融信托大厦（原北京开元名都大酒店）和百盛太阳宫写字楼（原百盛太阳宫店）来看，中植系擅长的“商改办”改造方案在“工3”项目中并不好操作，毕竟“工3”目前还属于公寓式住宅，虽然土地性质涵盖商业及办公，但建筑本身的层高、损旧及瑕疵等限制了商业属性的开发。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">但是，此次中海晟融与世茂集团的合作或许可以很好的解决“工3”物业属性的这一阻碍，毕竟世茂集团在前世茂工三的运营中已攒足对区域开发及运作的经验，与此同时“工3”项目自身对世茂在上市后进一步扩张地产及商业开发也有很大的帮助，世茂既然加入此次“工3”项目运作，定然会拿出自己所擅长的地产和商业开发本领，助力“工3”重放异彩，我们也将拭目以待。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">时隔13年，借助中植系这强大资本的注入，世茂重回三里屯续写他的“工体”情缘，就北京市商业区域的规划，三里屯“工体”犹如他所处的位置，夜晚的霓虹与白天的繁华从未停止，正如北京市场那些从未停滞的资产，只要北京还有个三里屯，“工体”情缘的故事就会一直被续写。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">【版权声明】：我们尊重原创，也注重分享。有部分内容来自互联网，版权归原作者所有，仅供学习参考之用，禁止用于商业用途，如无意侵犯原创媒体、公司 、企业或个人等的知识产权，请联系删除，本公众平台将不承担任何责任。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">【免责声明】：本平台对转载、分享的内容、陈述、观点判断保持中立，不对所包含内容的准确性、可靠性或完善性提供任何明示或暗示的保证，仅供读者参考，本公众平台将不承担任何责任。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">以上声明内容的最终解释权归本公司所有，本平台发表的文章将不再一一备注，本声明将适用本平台所有时间分享与转载文章，谢谢您的合作！</span></p></section>', 0, '1920', '2020-05-12 13:59:51', '2020-05-20 10:57:24', 0, 1);
INSERT INTO `la_news` VALUES (6, 4, 'SOHO中国闪跌25%背后的故事', NULL, 'JORCO云资产', NULL, NULL, '<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><section><section><section><img class=\" __bg_gif\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/gULw5FTH7H7skAcIicPIfND9Sm2mdP7k3osLtgzjqM4FeuKQS0XZBLmcH5icEiakqrxa9ryhrFEez1LecWlE52BPQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">5月4日， SOHO中国以2.75港元/股报收，跌幅25.68%，成为港股世上又一次闪跌事件。而距离SOHO中国3月10日暴涨的紧急停牌仅不足2月，纵观2个月SOHO中国的跌宕起伏，或许是成也“私有化”，败也“私有化”。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/gULw5FTH7H7skAcIicPIfND9Sm2mdP7k3WtzRC6aVyvPM5ZqMprZH57xJP0AF5kChgOIOWBClcdWbA6cA4F1oqw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">SOHO中国的暴跌暴涨如出一辙</strong></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">3月9日，港股市场传闻黑石集团正与SOHO中国就后者私有化进行谈判，交易价值40亿美元，黑石提出的私有化价格为每股6港元，并且交易细节预计将在未来几周内敲定。仅隔几个小时候，SOHO中国的股价于3月10日直线跳涨37.58%并触发暂停交易，次日仍继续一度大幅冲高。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">3月11日晚间，SOHO中国在港交所公告称，尚未就是否进行潜在交易作出决定，而且并未与任何一方订立实施潜在交易的正式协议．．．公司无法肯定任何此类洽谈（如继续进行）将导致对股份作出全面要约。”随后股价逐步震荡回落。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/gULw5FTH7H7skAcIicPIfND9Sm2mdP7k3t294MwQ7qb1JWOjpVwsUVW4vn1ia1SshUNGOj44tMRqpTDw3Vib08AFw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">5月4日， SOHO中国以2.75港元/股报收，跌幅25.68%，市场揣测与盛传“由于前景充满不确定性，黑石集团关于SOHO中国私有化的洽谈暂停”的消息有关。虽然5月5日复盘后股价反弹则与市场消极情绪有所缓和有关，但有意思的是，SOHO中国此轮股价的暴跌暴涨也与前不久的那轮股价走势如出一辙。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“私有化”或是为了抽身更彻底</strong></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">SOHO中国前身为红石实业，是潘石屹与其妻张欣共同创立。创立之初，SOHO中国以开发商业地产为主，但自2012年开始，SOHO中国从“销售”转向“自持”物业，其主要收入来源便从卖楼转为收租。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/gULw5FTH7H7skAcIicPIfND9Sm2mdP7k3wWx8qVohwVO89hIfDKScWWzy3HwIHKicnMibic0ZkiaWK3K6BQor99R5YQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">5月4日， SOHO中国以2.75港元/股报收，跌幅25.68%，市场揣测与盛传“由于前景充满不确定性，黑石集团关于SOHO中国私有化的洽谈暂停”的消息有关。虽然5月5日复盘后股价反弹则与市场消极情绪有所缓和有关，但有意思的是，SOHO中国此轮股价的暴跌暴涨也与前不久的那轮股价走势如出一辙。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">从SOHO中国3月25日公布的2019年年报看，其2019年营收18.47亿元人民币，同比增长11%。该收入全部来自其旗下物业租金收入。但其净利润下跌逾30%，2019年平均出租率为90%，较2018年96%出现下滑。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">但这似乎不足以引发SOHO中国盘中急跌。市场人士指出，急跌原因，或许与其私有化生变有关。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2014年，以82.8亿元出售上海的SOHO海伦广场、SOHO静安广场以及凌空SOHO部分物业</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2015年，以84.93亿元出售所持上海外滩国际金融中心8-1地块50%股权；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2016年，以32.2亿元出售上海的SOHO世纪广场；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2017年，以85.8亿元出售上海虹口SOHO以及凌空SOHO剩余物业面；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2018年，SOHO中国原总裁阎岩加盟黑石集团，出任集团亚洲房地产部董事总经理一职。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2019年，潘石屹一个月内注册了7家公司，且公司股东均为注册在境外的公司，注册资本从150万元至2亿元不等。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(50, 50, 50);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">自2014年至今，不完全统计显示，本次交易之前，SOHO中国已经套现的资产高达300亿元。</strong></span></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">外资更看好中国商业地产市场</strong></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">SOHO中国在2019年年报中曾提到，2020年海内外都会面临诸多影响经济的不确定性因素，但相信中国还会继续推动经济结构转型，并维持稳定的增长。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">从SOHO中国3月25日公布的2019年年报看，其2019年营收18.47亿元人民币，同比增长11%。该收入全部来自其旗下物业租金收入。但其净利润下跌逾30%，2019年平均出租率为90%，较2018年96%出现下滑。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/gULw5FTH7H7skAcIicPIfND9Sm2mdP7k3uqN5XawFgDiaMjpVYTBNpb2pFHvfhtaTzia3nPUIhXkzFvD7aQC8BvNg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">对于SOHO中国与黑石集团洽谈战略合作的传闻，其实黑石集团在近2年一直非常关注中国市场，出于全球资产配置的考虑，黑石在中国收购了多个商业项目，且对中国商业地产市场的发展前景抱有信心。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">世邦魏理仕此前发布的报告显示，2019年，北京物业投资大宗交易总额达到创历史纪录的866亿元，同比增长68%，首次超过上海，成为全国总成交额最高城市。其中，境外投资者是北京市场最为活跃的买家类型，投资额达到271亿元，占比达到31%，并在近两年保持上升势头。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/gULw5FTH7H7skAcIicPIfND9Sm2mdP7k3CibQWBTnHq5Go7J6eibgQwRxgCNazIZSu3S3AEuWTdWicpibrZAlbc4ftA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">戴德梁行发起投资者意向调查结果显示，超60%的受访者认为投资活动将在疫情结束后6个月内得到反弹，并有99%的受访者表示疫情过后依然会投资国内。城市方面，投资者对一线城市热情更为高昂，其中尤以外资为甚，100%外资受访者均表示未来12个月内有投资上海的计划。戴德梁行指出，对外资而言，投资中国大陆是全球资产布局，是长期的计划。所以短期的疫情影响有限，一旦市场恢复，投资者将继续投资中国大陆。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/gULw5FTH7H7skAcIicPIfND9Sm2mdP7k3Tj5gW8oOGWV5rWPv5c09x83MKxd8FibcDwlt1ZuskzsxM8MpCibrUaPw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" class=\"\"/>&nbsp;<section><section><br/></section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><section><section><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/zxYXZqpeA0AGCuIEqZlSRHkKtXicPQNq58tC6DOwX5DsDtttibTxtuGQia98ibCfVibR8xVFFy0U5ibO94CdydQAicngQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">关注兆古云资产<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-bo